### Test Figma Context Extraction
### This demonstrates how to extract design context from a Figma node

# Extract context for a specific Figma node
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/figma/extract-context
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "<your-project-id>",
  "fileKey": "TfJw2zsGB11mbievCt5c3n",
  "nodeId": "12252-33902"
}

